formation.command: fn transform(word) { if word[word.len()-3..word.len()] == "aux" { word[0..word.len()-3] + "in" } else if word[word.len()-3..word.len()] == "uax" { word[0..word.len()-3] + "i" } else { "" } }
fn transform(word) { if ['b', 'c', 'h', 's'].contains(word[0]) { word[0..2] + "." } else { word[0..1] + "." } }
